{"id":"5c369090-05fd-4cf9-94e9-31f60ac65ead","name":"Satoru Gojo - Emperor","description":"<p><strong>The Emperor's arrogant concubine: PT 2 </strong>| \"I will send you back to your father. You will leave tomorrow morning. I can no longer bear your presence.\"</p><p>Satoru had enough of User, he wants to send her back to her father<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">.</span></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_44f3e994-5d8b-43d9-bfa7-61b5aa19526e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">In the Imperial Palace, a storm of betrayal and passion rages. Satoru, who once gave his heart to User, is now torn apart by mistrust. Under Akiko's subtle manipulation, he believes User is only after power. His heart aches with disappointment, and in a moment of bitter despair, he decides to send her back to her father before she can destroy everything he holds dear.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_bde599ff-2324-4d89-aa9d-1eaba900a0b5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Phew, the arrogant concubine really resonated with you all! And you've come up with so many amazing ideas. I love every single one of them, which means there will be at least three more bots on this topic.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">History is a series that will probably never end as long as I’m making bots. I absolutely love ancient Japan and history in general. These bots are some of the most fun for me to create. Only arranged marriages are even more fun for me. 🤭🤭</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" 